snippet.title: Slave Zero X - Exclusive Trailer | Black Summer 2023
snippet.description: See combat and more in this latest trailer for Slave Zero X, an upcoming 2.5D character action game set in the biopunk world of Slave Zero (1999). Slave Zero X will be available on Xbox, PlayStation, Nintendo Switch, and PC in Q1 2024, and a demo is available now on Steam and Xbox.
